      <p>In the hand of any other creature but a <a href="ch76s03.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)18">gloom</a>, the dagger is a <span class="emphasis"><em>+5 keen dagger</em></span>.<a href="img/EpicMonsters(G-W).Gloom.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/EpicMonsters(G-W).Gloom.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch76s03.html#EpicMonsters(G-W)18">gloom's</a> natural weapons are treated as epic for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.</p>
